Cell["\<\
Although following the same format that we\[CloseCurlyQuote]ve seen time and \
again, the above solution has the most extreme solution waves. It\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]s also important to note that the above solutions are \
mostly dependent on y as the waves propagate on the x axis indefinitely. \
